地自然會思考<br />\n我幫咗咁多人買旗就係得你一個有問題<br />\n係邊個有問題心照啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMB7qOu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMB7qOu.jpg&h=86786e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tupps1R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftupps1R.jpg&h=e8f98aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j4fLWVd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj4fLWVd.jpg&h=d9882f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xpukLOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxpukLOA.jpg&h=99fa6b3c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2860025b11a3bf8cf7c9ce711a15b67a26275712","tid":1600521,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"想請問而家仲有冇得訂"},{"pid":"aa87e17bf8fe6853edf1c41f0d1e37fcde214afe","tid":1600521,"uid":196560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2860025b11a3bf8cf7c9ce711a15b67a26275712","tid":1600521,"uid":3333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"想請問而家仲有冇得訂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T19:03:40.000Z","msg":"同上！！<br />\n仲有無得訂？"}]}